articles.title: China's largest private developer Country Garden warns of default - Financial Times
articles.description: Company has about $200bn in liabilities and close to $10bn in dollar-denominated debt
articles.content:
Country Garden, Chinas largest private developer, has warned of a potential default on its international debts in a significant blow to the countrys embattled property sector.
